Bumps <https://github.com/rubocop/rubocop|rubocop> from 1.57.0 to 1.57.1.

Release notes

_Sourced from <https://github.com/rubocop/rubocop/releases|rubocop's releases>._

> *RuboCop 1.57.1*
> *Bug fixes*
> 
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12271|#12271>: Fix a false positive for `Lint/RedundantSafeNavigation` when using snake case constant receiver. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12265|#12265>: Fix an error for `Layout/MultilineMethodCallIndentation` when usingarithmetic operation with block inside a grouped expression. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12177|#12177>: Fix an incorrect autocorrect for `Style/RedundantException`. (<https://github.com/ydah|`@​ydah`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12261|#12261>: Fix an infinite loop for `Layout/MultilineMethodCallIndentation` when multiline method chain with a block argument and method chain. (<https://github.com/ydah|`@​ydah`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12263|#12263>: Fix false positives for `Style/RedundantDoubleSplatHashBraces` when method call for no hash braced double splat receiver. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12262|#12262>: Fix an incorrect autocorrect for `Style/RedundantDoubleSplatHashBraces` when using double splat hash braces with `merge` method call twice. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)

Changelog

_Sourced from <https://github.com/rubocop/rubocop/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md|rubocop's changelog>._

> *1.57.1 (2023-10-13)*
> *Bug fixes*
> 
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12271|#12271>: Fix a false positive for `Lint/RedundantSafeNavigation` when using snake case constant receiver. ([<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>][])
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12265|#12265>: Fix an error for `Layout/MultilineMethodCallIndentation` when usingarithmetic operation with block inside a grouped expression. ([<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>][])
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12177|#12177>: Fix an incorrect autocorrect for `Style/RedundantException`. ([<https://github.com/ydah|`@​ydah`>][])
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12261|#12261>: Fix an infinite loop for `Layout/MultilineMethodCallIndentation` when multiline method chain with a block argument and method chain. ([<https://github.com/ydah|`@​ydah`>][])
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12263|#12263>: Fix false positives for `Style/RedundantDoubleSplatHashBraces` when method call for no hash braced double splat receiver. ([<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>][])
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12262|#12262>: Fix an incorrect autocorrect for `Style/RedundantDoubleSplatHashBraces` when using double splat hash braces with `merge` method call twice. ([<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>][])
